Class Message

java.lang.Object
  wsintelliauction.lib.net.message.Message
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
BidMessage, InfoMessage, QueryMessage, SolutionMessage
public abstract class Message
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Super-class for all message types. A message is an object which is used for communication via a network connection. Various message types exist:

Message types:

  • RAW
  • INFO
  • PLACEBID
  • QUERY
  • SOLUTION_OFFER
  • SOLUTION_ACCEPT
  • LEASE
  • CONFIRM_LEASE

James Lewis, Matthew Marlin
